"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:5.18.2\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">5.18.2</span> 标题：筐子、篮子、伊法（basket）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：אֵיפָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：’eyfah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:36\">EXO 16:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev5:11\">LEV 5:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev6:13\">LEV 6:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:36\">LEV 19:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num5:15\">NUM 5:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num28:5\">NUM 28:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut25:14\">DEU 25:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut25:14\">DEU 25:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut25:15\">DEU 25:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:19\">JDG 6:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:17\">RUT 2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:24\">1SA 1:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:17\">1SA 17:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:10\">PRO 20:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:10\">PRO 20:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:10\">ISA 5:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:10\">EZK 45:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:11\">EZK 45:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:11\">EZK 45:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:13\">EZK 45:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:13\">EZK 45:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:24\">EZK 45:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:24\">EZK 45:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:24\">EZK 45:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek46:5\">EZK 46:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek46:5\">EZK 46:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek46:7\">EZK 46:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek46:7\">EZK 46:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek46:7\">EZK 46:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek46:11\">EZK 46:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek46:11\">EZK 46:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek46:11\">EZK 46:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek46:14\">EZK 46:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:5\">AMO 8:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:10\">MIC 6:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech5:6\">ZEC 5:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech5:7\">ZEC 5:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech5:8\">ZEC 5:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech5:9\">ZEC 5:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech5:10\">ZEC 5:10</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：דּוּד</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：dud, dudai)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs10:7\">2KI 10:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps81:7\">PSA 81:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer24:1\">JER 24:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer24:2\">JER 24:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer24:2\">JER 24:2</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：טֶנֶא</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：tene’)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:2\">DEU 26:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:4\">DEU 26:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:5\">DEU 28:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:17\">DEU 28:17</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：כְּלוּב</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：kluv)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:27\">JER 5:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:1\">AMO 8:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:2\">AMO 8:2</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：סַל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：sal, salsiloth)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:16\">GEN 40:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:17\">GEN 40:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:17\">GEN 40:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:18\">GEN 40:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:3\">EXO 29:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:3\">EXO 29:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:23\">EXO 29:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:32\">EXO 29:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:2\">LEV 8:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:26\">LEV 8:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:31\">LEV 8:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num6:15\">NUM 6:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num6:17\">NUM 6:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num6:19\">NUM 6:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:19\">JDG 6:19</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：תֵּבָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：tevah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod2:3\">EXO 2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod2:5\">EXO 2:5</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：κόφινος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：kofinos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:20\">MAT 14:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:9\">MAT 16:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:43\">MRK 6:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:19\">MRK 8:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:17\">LUK 9:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:13\">JHN 6:13</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：σαργάνη</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：sarganē)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:33\">2CO 11:33</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：σπυρίς</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：spuris)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:37\">MAT 15:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:10\">MAT 16:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:8\">MRK 8:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:20\">MRK 8:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:25\">ACT 9:25</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0495_basket.jpg\" alt=\"用于储存和运输货物的大型编织篮\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">用于储存和运输货物的大型编织篮 (© Habib M’henni, CC BY-SA 3.0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>篮子是用草或芦苇等编织材料做成的一种容器。根据用途的不同，篮子的大小也有很大的不同。篮子可以盛装各种各样的东西，包括食物和农产品，甚至可以用来搬运泥土。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>希伯来文<em>’eyfah</em> 有时指一个体积单位（伊法），有时指具有该容量的篮子。翻译者要特别注意语境。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech5:7\">ZEC 5:7</a> 提到一种用来盖篮子（希伯来文<em>kikar</em> ）的东西。经文记载这个物品是用铅做的，并且篮子通常没有它。大多数译本将这个词译为“铅做的盖子”（“lid made of lead”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> ）或“铅盖”（“lead cover”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"God&#x27;s Word Translation\">GW</abbr> ）。</p>\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/OAI-0082_basket_with_fruits.png\" alt=\"OAI-0082_basket_with_fruits\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\"> (Image generated by ChatGPT using OpenAI technology)</figcaption></figure>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:27\">JER 5:27</a> 中，希伯来文<em>kluv</em> 似乎指的是一种非常特别的篮子；实际上，这是一种用来装鸟的笼子。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 把这节经文的开头译为“Like a basket full of birds”（“像装满鸟的篮子”），这暗示鸟已经死了。然而，大多数其他译本并没有译为“篮子”，而是译成“笼子”，似乎更好地保留了前一节经文的比喻。另一方面，在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:1\">AMO 8:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:2\">AMO 8:2</a> 中，<em>kluv</em> 一词毫无疑问是“容器”的统称，译文应该尽量使用一般性的词语，该词语所表示的物品应该适合用来在市场售卖、携带或存放水果。如果目标语言没有适合的篮子，那么可以译作任何作此用途的容器。</p>\n<p>对于上文所列三个在新约中表示篮子的词语，我们无法准确说明它们的意思有什么区别。希腊文<em>sarganē</em> 一词仅出现在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:33\">2CO 11:33</a> ，这显然是一个相当大的篮子，因为保罗就是坐在里面从大马士革的城墙缒下来的。在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:25\">ACT 9:25</a> 中，希腊文<em>spuris</em> 也指同一种篮子。</p>\n<p>对于希腊文<em>spuris</em> 和<em>kofinos</em> ，翻译者通常很难找到令人满意的对等词，因为在不同的目标语言中，特定类型的篮子有非常具体的名称；篮子的结构和大小不同，名称也不同。遗憾的是，我们无法从希腊文本中准确地知道篮子的大小或类型。翻译者要注意，选定的词语不能表示由塑料或橡胶等现代材料制成的容器。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
